title: Amazonia
info:
Used in the Quartz Summer Conference Demo http://bitworld.bitfellas.org/demo.php?id=12470

This Octamed tune was created when Thunderbolt was in Cybernetix, but the demo was released after he left. (To Thunderbolt's disapproval)

Also used in Audio Dreams by Chaos under the title "Amazonia" http://bitworld.bitfellas.org/demo.php?id=8099
